1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,500
Hey, did you hear about what happened to Sarah?

2
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:06,200
No, what happened? Is she okay?

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:09,000
She got that promotion she's been
working toward for months.

4
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:11,500
That's amazing! She totally deserves it.

5
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:14,000
I know, right? She's been staying late
every night this past quarter.

6
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:16,800
Well, hard work pays off.
I'm really happy for her.

7
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,500
We should throw her a party this weekend.

8
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:22,000
Great idea! I'll talk to the others
and figure out the details.

9
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:24,500
Make sure to keep it a surprise though.

10
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,000
Of course! Mum's the word.
